languages.text: Настоятель Гектархиус, помолишися, обратил взор свой в прошлое в поисках наставления.
After a prayer, the Prelate Hectarchius turned his eye to the past in search of instruction.

languages.text: Tras una oración, el prelado Hectarchius dirigió su mente al pasado, buscando instrucción.
languages.original_text: After a prayer, the Prelate Hectarchius turned his eye to the past in search of instruction.

languages.text: 经过一番祈祷之后，赫克塔奇乌斯教长转过了目光，寻求指示。
languages.original_text: After a prayer, the Prelate Hectarchius turned his eye to the past in search of instruction.

languages.text: 祈りが終わると、上級聖職者ヘクターキウスは指示を求めて背後に視線を向けた。

languages.text: Nach einem Gebet richtete Prälat Hectarchius sein Auge in die Vergangenheit, um Anweisungen zu erhalten.
languages.original_text: After a prayer, the Prelate Hectarchius turned his eye to the past in search of instruction.

traits.locale_text: ... richtete sein Auge in die Vergangenheit, um Anweisungen zu erhalten.

languages.text: Sa prière terminée, le prélat Hectarchius se tourne vers le passé à la recherche d'un enseignement.
